OL,3,CSouthport riots review finds police
OL,4,Cunderestimated risk of disorder
OL,6,FPolice failed to realise the
OL,7,Fsignificance of a series of precursor
OL,8,Fevents leading up to the summer riots
OL,9,Fand there were gaps in intelligence
OL,10,Flinked to social media and the dark
OL,11,Fweb, a watchdog has claimed.
OL,13,FHis Majesty's Inspectorate of
OL,14,FConstabulary and Fire and Rescue
OL,15,FServices (HMICFRS) published a new
OL,16,Freport on Wednesday on how police
OL,17,Fforces dealt with disorder that broke
OL,18,Fout after the murder of three girls at
OL,19,Fa holiday dance class in Southport.
