OL,3,CSouthport riots review finds police
OL,4,Cunderestimated risk of disorder
OL,6,FIt found that a number of events in
OL,7,F2023 and 2024 were indicators of
OL,8,Fpotential future disorder, but this
OL,9,Fhad not been reflected in police
OL,10,Fintelligence assessments.
OL,12,FThe report said: "We have found that
OL,13,Fthe series of incidents of violence
OL,14,Fand disorder across the UK during 2023
OL,15,Fand 2024 should have influenced the
OL,16,Fpolice service's assessments of threat
OL,17,Fand risk.
