OL,3,CSouthport riots review finds police
OL,4,Cunderestimated risk of disorder
OL,6,FThe incidents highlighted included:
OL,7,Fdisorder near asylum seeker hotels in
OL,8,FMerseyside and Rotherham in February
OL,9,F2023, and from July to October in
OL,10,FLlanelli.
OL,12,FRiots broke out after two teenagers
OL,13,Fdied in an e-bike crash in May in Ely,
OL,14,FCardiff, and in November there was
OL,15,Fviolence as protesters clashed over
OL,16,FArmistice Day weekend in London.
