OL,3,CSouthport riots review finds police
OL,4,Cunderestimated risk of disorder
OL,6,FIn April 2024 disorder broke out at a
OL,7,FSt George's Day parade in London, and
OL,8,Frival protesters clashed during a
OL,9,Fdemonstration organised by Tommy
OL,10,FRobinson in June.
OL,12,FThe few weeks before the post-
OL,13,FSouthport disorder saw unrest in
OL,14,FHarehills, Leeds; the stabbing of a
OL,15,Fsoldier in Kent; and a protest in
OL,16,FRotherham over footage of police
OL,17,Fofficers using force while making
OL,18,Farrests at Manchester Airport.
