OL,3,CSouthport riots review finds police
OL,4,Cunderestimated risk of disorder
OL,6,FThere was also another mass rally
OL,7,Forganised by Tommy Robinson in London
OL,8,Fon July 27.
OL,10,FThe report also found that police
OL,11,Fchiefs brought in a system where
OL,12,Fofficers are moved between forces to
OL,13,Fbolster resources too late.
OL,15,FIt recommended that the protocol
OL,16,Fshould have been brought in on Friday
OL,17,FAugust 2, particularly as it was the
OL,18,Fstart of the weekend and the weather
OL,19,Fwas forecast to be good.
