OL,3,CSouthport riots review finds police
OL,4,Cunderestimated risk of disorder
OL,6,FThe system was not brought in until
OL,7,Ffour days later, meaning that there
OL,8,Fwere too many incidents where static
OL,9,Flines of officers were being pelted
OL,10,Fwith missiles and there were not
OL,11,Fenough of them to arrest
OL,12,Ftroublemakers, the watchdog found.
OL,14,FChief Inspector of Constabulary Andy
OL,15,FCooke said: "We found the police
OL,16,Fdecisions to co-ordinate and mobilise
OL,17,Fthose public order officers nationally
OL,18,Fwere made too late, and the police
OL,19,Fdidn't have a proper intelligence
OL,20,Fpicture of the rising tide of violence.
