OL,3,CSouthport riots review finds police
OL,4,Cunderestimated risk of disorder
OL,6,FIn total, 302 officers were injured
OL,7,Fduring the unrest, of whom 54 were
OL,8,Fadmitted to hospital. The day with the
OL,9,Flargest number deployed was August 10,
OL,10,Fwhen 6,675 public order officers were
OL,11,Fon duty.
OL,13,FMr Cooke has called for a national co-
OL,14,Fordinator put in charge who could
OL,15,Finstruct forces to provide mutual aid
OL,16,Fand said some chief constables had
OL,17,Fdragged their feet over doing so.
OL,19,FThere were also concerns about some
OL,20,Fofficers being sent out in regular
OL,21,Funiform rather than riot gear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
