OL,6,FMr Cooke said: "I doubt it will be
OL,7,Fanother 14 years before we see serious
OL,8,Fdisorder. I hope it is, but I doubt it.
OL,10,F"I think we're in a different place,
OL,11,Fthere are far more tensions across
OL,12,Fcommunities and far more ways of
OL,13,Fsharing information across the
OL,14,Fcommunity.
OL,16,F"So policing needs to ensure that it's
OL,17,Fready for whenever that next disorder
OL,18,Fwill be."
