OL,6,FMr Cooke said while the systems under
OL,7,Fwhich officers operate need to change,
OL,8,Fthey should be praised for the way
OL,9,Fthey handled the riots.
OL,11,F"Officers displayed immense bravery in
OL,12,Fthe face of extreme violence. It is to
OL,13,Ftheir enormous credit that they kept
OL,14,Fthe public safe.
OL,16,F"Many police officers sustained
OL,17,Finjuries, and some were hospitalised.
OL,19,F"The violence officers suffered is
OL,20,Fshameful and unacceptable. They
OL,21,Fdeserve the public's full support."
